{"tid":2235782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［眾新聞回帶］興德學校前校長疑偽造文件 虛報學生等5宗違規只發出警告信 反而一張工作紙就要釘牌","createTime":"2020-10-09T03:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T05:52:19.000Z","uid":22556,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5b957d5dc5fe6e73961493d1dfd347338ffd7c05","tid":2235782,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k969eVk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk969eVk.jpg&h=05834a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【回帶】興德學校前校長陳章萍涉5宗嚴重違規　教育局僅發警告信<br />\n<br />\n九龍城宣道小學一名資深老師，因為負責編製一個2小時課節的教材，被教育局指控散播港獨訊息，裁定「嚴重專業失德」，遭取消教師註冊，是首次有教師被指專業失德而被釘牌。<br />\n<br />\n回帶到2017年，屯門興德學校爆發醜聞，前校長陳章萍被指虛報「影子學生」、懷疑偽造文件、迫病假老師交餅卡等，警方、廉署及私隱專員公署介入調查事件，引起軒然大波。不過，據傳媒報導，當時教育局僅向陳章萍發警告信，當中指陳嚴重違規，並力數她五宗罪，包括未有呈報缺課個案；安排教師於正常上課時段到深圳派傳單招生；濫權欺壓教師；未有按教育局要求暫緩處理兩位被解僱老師的指示；向教育局提供虛假資料。陳章萍因涉嫌向教育局出示虛假面試紀錄，被控一項使用虛假文書罪，去年被裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－<br />\n亼 緊貼眾新聞 亼<br />\nFollow TG：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkcnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkcnews&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=0506dd92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkcnews</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zykNXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zykNXc&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=26d51d4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zykNXc</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37AfYcp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37AfYcp&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=922e9212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37AfYcp</a><br />\nYouTube：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37A1PMI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37A1PMI&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=ae697724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37A1PMI</a><br />\n－－－－－－－－<br />\n現在訂閱眾新聞一年或以上，送柳俊江新書《元朗黑夜 ── 我的記憶和眾人的記憶》或譚蕙芸新書《天愈黑，星愈亮 ── 反修例運動的人和事》，二選一：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/訂閲我們\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F%E8%A8%82%E9%96%B2%E6%88%91%E5%80%91&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=a55e2539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/訂閲我們</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1283142602029146/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366243453719070%2Fposts%2F1283142602029146%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=326f0e88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1283142602029146/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"0db7bf063530bf1e8e6992c4969a1d2ee3d3becd","tid":2235782,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:25:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"984cce3dbf08dabb671ce5f6deb121b5be8ed8d9","tid":2235782,"uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:27:01.000Z","msg":"呢隻肥豬之前話入精神病院搏同情<br />\n而家點？<br />\n<br />\n屌我覺得香港人應該要整返個香港小氣薄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1827d09669068914f8f97260b3c627bf4ef9fb8e","tid":2235782,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729e265629c2391f5185c84e9c559a4f6224a431","tid":2235782,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 